>感<rp>(</rp><rt>かん</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>じがします。','Ben ga shitai kanji ga shimasu.','I feel like I need to pass stool. (a key sign)','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2593,491,15,'Staff say','nurse','まだいきまないでください。','まだいきまないでください。','Mada ikimanaide kudasai.','Do not push yet.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2594,491,16,'Staff say','nurse','内診をします。','<ruby>内診<rp>（</rp><rt>ないしん</rt><rp>）</rp></ruby>をします。','Naishin o shimasu.','I will do an internal examination.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2595,491,17,'Staff say','nurse','子宮口は五センチです。','<ruby>子宮<rp>(</rp><rt>しきゅう</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby><ruby>口<rp>(</rp><rt>ぐち</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>は<ruby>五<rp>(</rp><rt>ご</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>センチです。','Shikyuukou wa go-senchi desu.','The cervix is five centimeters.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2596,491,18,'Staff say','nurse','全開になりました。','<ruby>全開<rp>(</rp><rt>ぜんかい</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>になりました。','Zenkai ni narimashita.','She is fully dilated.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2597,491,19,'Staff say','nurse','お産は順調です。','お<ruby>産<rp>(</rp><rt>さん</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>は<ruby>順調<rp>(</rp><rt>じゅんちょう</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>です。','Osan wa junchou desu.','Labor is progressing well.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2598,491,20,'Staff say','nurse','モニターをつけます。','モニターをつけます。','Monitaa o tsukemasu.','I will attach the monitor.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2599,491,21,'Staff say','nurse','点滴をします。','<ruby>点滴<rp>(</rp><rt>てんてき</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>をします。','Tenteki o shimasu.','We will set up an IV drip.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2600,491,22,'Staff say','nurse','分娩室に移動します。','<ruby>分娩室<rp>（</rp><rt>ぶんべんしつ</rt><rp>）</rp></ruby>に<ruby>移動<rp>(</rp><rt>いどう</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>します。','Bunbenshitsu ni idou shimasu.','We are moving to the delivery room.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2601,491,23,'You','husband','立ち会ってもいいですか。','<ruby>立<rp>(</rp><rt>た</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>ち<ruby>会<rp>(