u owarimasu.','It is almost over.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2622,493,19,'Staff','doctor','上手です。','<ruby>上手<rp>(</rp><rt>じょうず</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>です。','Jouzu desu.','You are doing well.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2623,493,20,'Staff','doctor','その調子です。','その<ruby>調子<rp>(</rp><rt>ちょうし</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>です。','Sono choushi desu.','That is it, keep going.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2624,493,21,'Staff','doctor','生まれました！','<ruby>生<rp>(</rp><rt>う</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>まれました！','Umaremashita!','The baby is born!','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2625,493,22,'Staff','doctor','おめでとうございます。','おめでとうございます。','Omedetou gozaimasu.','Congratulations.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2626,493,23,'Staff','doctor','へその緒を切りますか。','<ruby>へその緒<rp>（</rp><rt>へそのお</rt><rp>）</rp></ruby>を<ruby>切<rp>(</rp><rt>き</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>りますか。','Heso no o o kirimasu ka.','Would you like to cut the cord?','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2627,493,24,'Staff','doctor','胎盤を出します。','<ruby>胎盤<rp>(</rp><rt>たいばん</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>を<ruby>出<rp>(</rp><rt>だ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>します。','Taiban o dashimasu.','We will deliver the placenta.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2628,493,25,'Staff','doctor','傷を縫います。','<ruby>傷<rp>(</rp><rt>きず</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>を<ruby>縫<rp>(</rp><rt>ぬ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>います。','Kizu o nuimasu.','We will stitch the tear.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2629,494,1,'You','husband','がんばって。','がんばって。','Ganbatte.','Hang in there.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2630,494,2,'You','husband','がんばって！',NULL,'Ganbatte!','You can do it!','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2631,494,3,'You','husband','よくがんばっていますよ。','よくがんばっていますよ。','Yoku ganbatte imasu yo.','You are doing so well.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2632,494,4,'You','husband','あと少しですよ。','あと<ruby>少<rp>(</rp><rt>すこ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>しですよ。','Ato sukoshi desu yo.','Just a little more.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2633,494,5,'You','husband','大丈夫です、大丈夫ですよ。','<ruby>大丈夫<rp>(</rp><rt>だいじょうぶ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>です、<ruby>大丈夫<rp>(</rp><rt>だいじょうぶ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>ですよ。','Daijoubu desu, daijoubu desu yo.','It is okay, it is okay.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2634,494,6,'You','husband','そばにいますよ。','そばにいますよ。','Soba ni imasu yo.','I am right beside you.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2635,494,7,'You','husband','ずっと一緒ですよ。','ずっと<ruby>一緒<rp>(</rp><rt>いっしょ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>ですよ。','Zutto issho desu yo.','I will be with you the whole time.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2636,494,8,'You','husband','手を握りますね。','<ruby>手<rp>(</rp><rt>て</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>を<ruby>握<rp>(</rp><rt>にぎ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>りますね。','Te o nigirimasu ne.','I will hold your hand.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2637,494,9,'You','husband','強く握っていいですよ。','<ruby>強<rp>(</rp><rt>つよ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>く<ruby>握<rp>(</rp><rt>にぎ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>っていいですよ。','Tsuyoku nigitte ii desu yo.','You can squeeze hard.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2638,494,10,'You','husband','一緒に呼吸しましょう。','<ruby>一緒<rp>(</rp><rt>いっしょ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>に<ruby>呼吸<rp>(</rp><rt>こきゅう</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>しましょう。','Issho ni kokyuu shimashou.','Let us breathe together.','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2639,494,11,'You','husband','すって……はいて……。','すって……はいて……。','Sutte…… haite…….','In…… out…….','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2640,494,12,'You','husband','腰をさすりましょうか。','<ruby>腰<rp>(</rp><rt>こし</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>をさすりましょうか。','Koshi o sasurimashou ka.','Shall I rub your back?','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2641,494,13,'You','husband','水を飲みますか。','<ruby>水<rp>(</rp><rt>みず</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>を<ruby>飲<rp>(</rp><rt>の</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>みますか。','Mizu o nomimasu ka.','Do you want some water?','2026-07-12 20:17:36','2026-07-12 20:17:36'),(2642,494,14,'You','husband','氷はどうですか。','<ruby>氷<rp>(</r